Hi @Haj Suma / @Gene Siepka , I see Beyla can be deployed without enabling privileged access, but it needs specific capabilities to be enabled. Can you please give the required permissions to deploy.


        securityContext:
          capabilities:
            add:
            - BPF
            - SYS_PTRACE
            - NET_RAW
            - CHECKPOINT_RESTORE
            - DAC_READ_SEARCH
            - PERFMON
            - SYS_ADMIN
            - NET_ADMIN
            drop:
            - ALL
          readOnlyRootFilesystem: true
          runAsUser: 0
      hostNetwork: true
